title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Monday Night Football games. What's the biggest factor in the success we've seen with Josh Allen and Jalen Hurts this season? The guys have an Alabama QB Draft. And Pro Football HOFer Michael Strahan shares which is harder, hosting GMA or playing football in the NFL.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
